review: Dr. Neha and Dr. Vidhi are great doctors, not only they are perfect at work but also very honest about treatment and go an extra mile to remove any doubt. I had lot of apprehensions about the treatment but within 2 sittings scaling and filling issues were sorted.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
Dr Neha has a calm, friendly and scientific approach. Dr Neha, Dr Srihari and Dr Fawad did an amazing job on my elderly father's teeth. They installed a full new set of teeth on implants that looks great and functions perfectly. It was particularly complex due to my father's age, Parkinsons-related tremors and other health issues. Their patience helped him remain calm throughout the procedures. 

Thanks to this procedure he is finally able to eat solid food after a year and this has helped his overall recovery. 

We are very grateful to Dr Neha, Dr Srihari and Dr Fawad and it is due to their skills, knowledge and the efforts they went to above and beyond (including coming home when my father could not travel) that makes medicine such a noble profession. 

I strongly recommend Dr Neha and her colleagues.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: It was so perfect and everything was right. I had pain in my wisdom teeth over last 6-8 months. I was so very concerned and afraid to visit a dentist. Dr Neha has been very friendly, she diagnosed the problem well and explained the different options possible. The wisdom teeth had been problematic over 6-8 months and extraction was one good option. The entire procedure was made as comfortable as possible. I am happy now that the extraction was done well, stitches removed after one week and I am all good now. The place is very clean, hygienic and bright. The doctors are super experts and support stuff know what they need to do. ******** **** ***** *** *** ****** ***********

tags: Doctor friendliness,Value for money,Treatment satisfaction,Explanation of the health issue,Wait time,
review: Dr Neha is a very friendly doctor, we visited her clinic for my mother-in-law's treatment. She treated us well and listens to the problems with patience. She suggested all the ways that we could take and performed the diagnosis to the core. She discussed everything even minute details around do's and dont's. Patient is a senior citizen and she suggested things that we should do to avoid any damage in future because of old age and asked us to be proactive. That was quite useful in terms of planning. Clinic is well equipped and they are taking all covid precautions.

review: I visited the clinic for dental check up. Neha Sarda is very polite friendly to the point and caring dentist What ever possible for her she does. Neha Andhare is also a great dentist with proper sense and very polite friendly and humanly treatment. she verified every problem in entire teeth. One by one she started treatment. I being a senior citizen got very much comfortable with her and in small discussion she got my full confidence. I got fearless and requested her to treat every problem. She didn't insist for any treatment. First she asked me for filling in two teeth. I got painless treatment. During second visit she checked if Root canal treatment is required as was suggested by previous dentist. She came to the conclusion of filling only by composite materials. Only required painless treatment she did at very reasonable charges. Extremely brilliant in her job.
